text: Woodend is a town in the Waimakariri District, New Zealand. It is situated 25 kilometers north of Christchurch and 6.6 kilometers north of Kaiapoi, 6.3 kilometers east of Rangiora and is a walking distance from Peagsus. It has a primary school and has two beaches located near the town. == References == Category:Towns in Canterbury Region Category:Waimakariri District
title: Woodend, New Zealand
